Am I leaking, or just doing something wrong?
Also, is anyone in CA having a problem getting their tank filled because of
the "improper" valve?
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
That regulation ONLY affects portable barbeque tanks. Go here and print this:
 http://www.recvehicle.com/propane.html
If someone is giving you a hard time then have them READ the 1st sentence
where it says VERTICAL and NON-STATIONARY. Your tank on your bus is HORIZONTAL
and permanently mounted. It is NOT a portable tank.
